{"tid":1947176,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《禁蒙面法》違憲上訴，代表律師余若海： 憂武漢肺炎市民可戴外科口罩，強調有別「豬嘴」","createTime":"2020-03-28T06:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T08:26:39.000Z","uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"06119ede3d54bb3b7e95f4f6974057c08a70972f","tid":1947176,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:20:45.000Z","msg":"高院早前裁定《緊急法》及《禁蒙面法》違憲，頒令《禁蒙面法》無效，律政司一方不服裁決提出上訴，今於高等法院審理。<br />\n<br />\n代表律政司的資深大律師余若海陳詞指，最近武漢爆發不明肺炎，市民若擔心健康戴上一般外科醫療口罩，屬於《禁蒙面法》下的合理辯解，可不被視為犯法。<br />\n<br />\n他強調外科口罩與示威活動中黑衣人所佩戴的面罩大為不同，後者遮蓋全面，目的是防止吸入催淚煙等防暴用品，而<span style=\"color: red;\">配戴這些面罩的人士傾向於參與暴力活動及與警方衝突</span>。"},{"pid":"483e7af64de3811203713c8d7df465ce827cbd48","tid":1947176,"uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:20:55.000Z","msg":"N95 缺貨　醫管局研購「豬嘴」替代 有醫護擬自行購買　需消毒憂增感染風險<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1947148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1947148</a>"},{"pid":"6d8c77ef5156d1a734b2ebf075c3aad2fc511e5d","tid":1947176,"uid":68226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"483e7af64de3811203713c8d7df465ce827cbd48","tid":1947176,"uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:20:55.000Z","msg":"N95 缺貨　醫管局研購「豬嘴」替代 有醫護擬自行購買　需消毒憂增感染風險<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1947148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1947148</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:22:05.000Z","msg":"一陣間係醫院射tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c54812f07c72ccf61ebdb41c19d2295221b732d","tid":1947176,"uid":101481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:23:14.000Z","msg":"啱呀 睇下警犬戴左幾暴力"},{"pid":"4f5214ebc75c5d123b70a27c100b1172c1684399","tid":1947176,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6d8c77ef5156d1a734b2ebf075c3aad2fc511e5d","tid":1947176,"uid":68226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"483e7af64de3811203713c8d7df465ce827cbd48","tid":194